<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Cambria, serif; /* Set font to Cambria */
            color: #333; /* Set text color to dark */
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start; /* Align items at the start of the container */
            position: relative; /* Position relative for absolute positioning */
        }

        .content {
            display: flex; /* Display content flexibly */
            align-items: flex-start; /* Align items at the start of the content */
            padding: 20px;
        }

        img {
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-right: 20px; /* Add space between image and text box */
            height: 100%; /* Set image height to match text box */
        }

        .textbox {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* Semi-transparent background */
            border-radius: 8px; /* Rounded corners */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            height: 100%; /* Match height with the image */
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 0; /* Remove default margin for h2 */
            font-size: 28px; /* Increase font size of heading */
            font-weight: bold; /* Make heading bold */
        }

        .textbox p {
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Add spacing between text and button */
            font-size: 24px; /* Increase font size of the price text */
        }

        .checkout-btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff; /* Blue background */
            color: white; /* White text color */
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px; /* Add space between price and button */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold;">PC Parts</h2> <!-- Make text bold and slightly larger -->
                <p>PRODUCT NAME</p>
                <img src="~/Images/Framework-4k.png" alt="Paris" width="500" height="300">
            </div>
            <div class="textbox">
                <h2>PRODUCT NAME</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 30px;">$999</p> <!-- Increased font size of the price text -->
                <!-- Add any other content you want to display -->
                <button class="checkout-btn">Checkout</button> <!-- Checkout button -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>PRODUCT DETAILS AND SPECIFICATIONS HERE :


</body>
</html>

